- content_for :title, "Next Month's Recipe"
.container.content
  %h1 Next Month's Recipe
  %h4.muted January 2014
  .alert.alert-info
    The deadline to get January's kit is 1/17/14. If you missed the deadline, no worries! You are signed up for April.

  .alert.alert-info
    Kits will ship on Monday, January 20th.


  .well.well-large.monthly-recipe
    .row-fluid
      .span7
        %p.lead Winter Stout
        %p.desc Once again, it's it's cold outside!  In the spirit of the cold whether, this month's kit is a delicious Winter Stout.  We are sending this kit in January so you can brew and drink it while it's still winter. The kit will ship on Monday, January 20th, and you will receive it just before the weekend.  We hope you enjoy this January's kit and happy brewing!  Cheers!
      .span5.text-center
        = image_tag "gingerbread.jpg", class: "recipe-image"

